text: The Malaysia Design Archive (MDA) is an archive concerning design, located in Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia. ==History== The archive was established in 2008. ==See also== * List of tourist attractions in Malaysia ==References== ==External links== * Category:2008 establishments in Malaysia Category:Archives in Malaysia Category:Buildings and structures in Kuala Lumpur Category:Culture of Kuala Lumpur Category:Business and industry archives Category:Design history
